# Tabulate — Home Assistant integration

Companion integration for the **Tabulate** add-on. It adds a first-class
`tabulate.add_receipt` action that hands a scanned receipt image to the add-on
for OCR + AI extraction and categorization — so automations and Apple Shortcuts
(VisionKit document scans) can add receipts through Home Assistant's
authenticated API instead of ingress.

