## Setup

1. Install and start the **Tabulate** add-on from this repository.
2. Add the **Tabulate** integration (Settings → Devices & Services). It
   auto-detects the running add-on; otherwise enter its host and port manually.
3. Call the `tabulate.add_receipt` action. Pass a single `image_base64`, or a
   list via `images_base64` to add several receipts in one call. Set
   `wait_for_processing: false` for callers with short timeouts (e.g. Shortcuts).

See the repository README for the full Apple Shortcuts recipe.
